sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Restaurant Staff or Operations User
    participant UI as KhanaBook Interface
    participant KB as KhanaBook Backend
    participant EB as Easebuzz

    User->>UI: Request refund for paid order
    UI->>KB: Submit refund amount and reason
    KB->>KB: Validate payment, tenant, and refundable amount
    KB->>EB: Initiate refund
    EB-->>KB: Return refund identifier and status
    KB-->>UI: Show refund initiated
    EB-->>KB: Send refund status webhook
    KB->>KB: Verify webhook and update refund status

